				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>ikh hob geendikt di zeks-tege milkhome un dos iz geven mayn letste milkhome. dray milkhomes hob ikh mitgemakht in Yisroel.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
				</ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
